```plantuml
@startuml dwt0317_Search_Adserver

actor User
participant "SearchServlet" as SearchServlet
participant "ESServlet" as ESServlet
participant "BingServlet" as BingServlet
participant "AdRetrieval" as AdRetrieval
participant "QueryRewriter" as QueryRewriter
participant "ESHandler" as ESHandler
participant "DBPool" as DBPool
participant "RankingService" as RankingService
participant "Log4j" as Log4j

User -> SearchServlet: Submit search query
activate SearchServlet

SearchServlet -> ESServlet: Forward query (local search)
activate ESServlet
ESServlet -> ESHandler: Search documents
activate ESHandler
ESHandler --> ESServlet: Return search results
deactivate ESHandler
ESServlet --> SearchServlet: Return results
deactivate ESServlet

SearchServlet -> BingServlet: Forward query (Bing search)
activate BingServlet
BingServlet --> SearchServlet: Return Bing results
deactivate BingServlet

SearchServlet -> AdRetrieval: Retrieve ads for query
activate AdRetrieval

AdRetrieval -> QueryRewriter: Rewrite query
activate QueryRewriter
QueryRewriter --> AdRetrieval: Return rewritten query
deactivate QueryRewriter

AdRetrieval -> ESHandler: Get ads by keywords
activate ESHandler
ESHandler --> AdRetrieval: Return candidate ads
deactivate ESHandler

AdRetrieval -> DBPool: Get ad details
activate DBPool
DBPool --> AdRetrieval: Return ad metadata
deactivate DBPool

AdRetrieval -> RankingService: Rank ads (Thrift call)
activate RankingService
RankingService --> AdRetrieval: Return ranked ads
deactivate RankingService

AdRetrieval --> SearchServlet: Return ranked ads
deactivate AdRetrieval

SearchServlet -> Log4j: Log search request
activate Log4j
Log4j --> SearchServlet: Logging complete
deactivate Log4j

SearchServlet --> User: Display search results + ads

User -> SearchServlet: Click ad
activate SearchServlet
SearchServlet -> DBPool: Charge advertiser
activate DBPool
DBPool --> SearchServlet: Charge complete
deactivate DBPool

SearchServlet -> Log4j: Log click
activate Log4j
Log4j --> SearchServlet: Logging complete
deactivate Log4j
deactivate SearchServlet

@enduml
```